{"tid":39978,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"換鈔傷業績 印度富士康25%員工放假","createTime":"2016-12-15T01:41:53.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-15T06:44:56.000Z","uid":22675,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"93237249711ef061d612deeac52b311fefdd3b57","tid":39978,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-15T01:41:53.000Z","msg":"<strong>換鈔傷業績 印度富士康部分員工放有薪假</strong><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n據印度當地媒體報導，鴻海集團旗下組裝代工廠富士康提供25%員工放2周有薪假，因應印度政府廢大額紙鈔後導致業績腰斬的衝擊。<br />\n<br />\n據外電報導，印度政府上月初進行廢除500與1,000盧比大面額紙鈔後，<span style=\"color: red;\">導致該國面臨嚴重現金緊縮，受到現金短缺進而影響噹地民間消費</span>，導致當地品牌手機銷售大減，富士康印度廠受到連帶影響，當地業績大受衝擊，外電指富士康印度廠業績腰斬，迫使印度廠產量削減一半<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 。<br />\n<br />\n印度政府廢鈔政策導致當地手機產業產生骨牌效應，由於當地民眾消費主要以現金為主，且熱門手機售價約落在5000盧比，因此身受廢鈔政策影響。外電指出，印度當地手機廠如INTEX、LAVA、Karbonn因應需求短缺正規畫裁撤或縮減10-40%人力。<br />\n<br />\nlink:<a href=\"http://money.udn.com/money/story/5612/2163925\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fmoney.udn.com%2Fmoney%2Fstory%2F5612%2F2163925&d=B2WJE3X6oE5O%2BR%2BUVRX1FhpDoU409oZNeObLMRtCPuc%3D&h=af07a6e9\" target=\"_blank\">http://money.udn.com/money/story/5612/2163925</a>"},{"pid":"879a9b7abe945bf7189ccca5f4dc13cd50cd59c6","tid":39978,"uid":90,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-15T01:56:51.000Z","msg":"Ok"},{"pid":"a9b8ff5a4cad205a88565594596672d4ec114b81","tid":39978,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-15T05:20:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7271f10bacd9bdf7c772d78a8dba83d2b5636673","tid":39978,"uid":22736,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-15T05:28:10.000Z","msg":"富士康良心企業<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"581fae083430b3cfc1c2c699b2d4f97bc656fd3f","tid":39978,"uid":22422,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-15T06:25:38.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>富士康良心企業<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n係香港嘅話 港豬會點<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1790fb963e79fd7340cebe7b05028a003ee8c953","tid":39978,"uid":52215,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-15T06:44:56.000Z","msg":"富士康: 邊個撚樣叫我印度開廠<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/33.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}